24 // NOTE that the 0xFFFF of 0xFF entries at the end of some tables below are
25 // not properly list terminators, but are actually the printable definitions
26 // of values that are legitimately found on the PCI bus. The size
27 // definitions should be used for loop control when the table is searched.
28 
29 typedef struct _PCI_VENTABLE
30 {
31  unsigned short VenId ;
32  const char * VenShort ;
33  const char * VenFull ;
34 } PCI_VENTABLE, *PPCI_VENTABLE ;
